DOCUMENT();        # This should be the first executable line in the problem.

loadMacros(
"PG.pl",
"PGbasicmacros.pl",
"PGchoicemacros.pl",
"PGanswermacros.pl",
"PGauxiliaryFunctions.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$b =  random(2,4,1);
$c =  random(5,8,1);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
Find all solutions of the equation \( t + $b + \frac{$c}{t} = 0\) and
express them in the form \(a + b i\):
$BR $BR 
First input the solution with \(b <0\) here:
$BR
the real number \(a\) equals \{ans_rule(20) \} 
and the real number \( b \) equals \{ans_rule(20) \}
$BR
Then input the solution with \(b > 0\) here:
$BR
the real number \(a\) equals \{ans_rule(20) \} 
and the real number \( b \) equals \{ans_rule(20) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans1 = -$b/2;
$ans2 = -(-$b**2+4*$c)**(1/2)/2; 
$ans3 = -$b/2;
$ans4 = (-$b**2+4*$c)**(1/2)/2; 

ANS(num_cmp($ans1));
ANS(num_cmp($ans2));
ANS(num_cmp($ans3));
ANS(num_cmp($ans4));

ENDDOCUMENT();        # This should be the last executable line in the problem.

